  "text": "June 23, 2006 Notification No. 69/2006-CUSTOMS (N.T.) S.O. (E). - In exercise of the powers conferred by sub-section (1) of section 4 of the Customs Act, 1962 (52 of 1962), the Central Board of Excise and Customs hereby appoints the Commissioner of Customs (Imports), Jawahar Customs House, Nhava Sheva, Uran, Raigad, Maharashtra, to act as, - (i) Commissioner of Customs (Import), New Custom House, Ballard Estate, Mumbai; (ii) Commissioner of Customs (Export), New Custom House, Mumbai; for the purposes of adjudicating the matters relating to show cause notice pertaining to M/s. Vastupal Tejpal (India) and others issued, vide, DRI. F.No: DRI/MZU/C/INV-11/2004-05 dated 31.03.2005 by the Additional Director General, Directorate of Revenue Intelligence, Mumbai Zonal Unit, 3rd / 4th Floor, Hotel Waldorf Building, 16, Arthur Bunder Road, Colaba, Mumbai -400006. [F.NO.437/ 4 /2006-Cus.IV] -- 1 of 1 --",
